---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Don't Lose Your Way" description="I wrote a letter I hoped no one would ever have to read. I'm still here. And if you're reading this, you are too.">

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The Story</h1>
      <blockquote class="origin-quote">I wrote a letter I hoped no one would ever have to read.</blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container about-body">
      <div class="about-text">
        <p>I'm still here. And if you're reading this, you are too.</p>
        
        <p>Don't Lose Your Way wasn't born from a business plan. It was born from a moment — a moment where everything felt like it was closing in, where silence felt louder than words, and where the distance between where I was and where I needed to be seemed impossible to cross.</p>
        
        <p>I spent years not speaking. Not because I had nothing to say, but because I didn't know how to say it. The silence became a habit. The habit became a wall. And the wall almost became an ending.</p>
        
        <p>But someone called me back. And I walked away from that bridge.</p>
        
        <p>This space exists for people who almost gave up — and stayed. It's not therapy. It's not a fix. It's proof that others have stood where you stand. Sometimes that's enough. Sometimes it's just enough to keep going for one more day.</p>
        
        <p>Don't Lose Your Way is a place to breathe. To write what you're feeling. To turn those feelings into something you can hear — words, lyrics, songs. Some things are shared. Some things stay private. But every voice matters.</p>
        
        <p>If you're in crisis right now, please reach out:</p>
        
        <div class="crisis-box">
          <p><strong>Call or text <a href="tel:988">988</a></strong></p>
          <p>24/7 • Free • Confidential</p>
          <p>Suicide & Crisis Lifeline</p>
        </div>

        <p>You don't have to carry this alone. You never did.</p>
        
        <p class="signature">— The person who walked back</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
  }

  .origin-quote {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    max-width: 30rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .origin-quote { font-size: 1.75rem; }
  }

  .about-body {
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .crisis-box {
    background: rgba(239,68,68,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(239,68,68,0.3);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .crisis-box p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem !important;
    color: white !important;
  }

  .crisis-box a {
    color: var(--color-crisis);
    text-decoration: underline;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .signature {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle) !important;
    margin-top: 2rem !important;
  }
</style>